amerigeddon is a 2016 american action film directed by mike norris and written by gary heavin .   the movie describes a fictional attack on the united states by its own government , working in concert with a global terrorist organization and the united nations .   heavin has said that he regards the events in the film as a " very real threat " .   the movie was shot on heavin 's central texas ranch and in nearby towns , and most cast members were recruited locally .   the movie was released on may 13 , 2016 .   the plot of amerigeddon bears a resemblance to that of red dawn .